@startuml AmnisIO_AmnisIO

[AmnisIO CLI] as CLI
[typewriter] as Transpiler
[PlatformIO] as PIO
[rivulet] as StreamLib
[gyrus] as BoardAbstraction
[TypeScript Code] as TSCode
[C Code] as CCode
[Hardware] as HW

CLI --> Transpiler : uses
CLI --> PIO : integrates
CLI --> StreamLib : includes
CLI --> BoardAbstraction : includes

Transpiler --> TSCode : reads
Transpiler --> CCode : generates

PIO --> CCode : builds & deploys

StreamLib --> CCode : provides reactive primitives
BoardAbstraction --> CCode : provides hardware abstraction

CCode --> HW : controls

note right of CLI
  Orchestrates build
  and deployment process
end note

note right of Transpiler
  Converts TypeScript
  to C code
end note

note right of StreamLib
  Enables reactive
  programming
end note

note right of BoardAbstraction
  Abstracts hardware-specific
  functionality
end note

@enduml